b-date><volume>39</volume><issue>1</issue><fpage>19</fpage><lpage>36</lpage><history><date date-type="received"><day>30</day><month>09</month><year>2019</year></date><date date-type="accepted"><day>18</day><month>02</month><year>2020</year></date></history><permissions><license license-type="open-access" xlink:href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" xml:lang="en"><license-p>This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License.</license-p></license></permissions><abstract><p>RESUMO A intenção do artigo é problematizar os significados históricos do termo/conceito periferia, esboçando algumas definições a partir do uso realizado pelos próprios moradores. O artigo também procura sistematizar o conceito sujeitas e sujeitos periféricos com base nos atributos que o conformam.</p></abstract><trans-abstract xml:lang="en"><p>ABSTRACT This article problematizes the historical meanings of the term/notion of periphery, outlining critical definitions that draw on empirical uses by residents of these spaces. The article also attempts to systematize the concept of peripheral subjects.</p></trans-abstract><kwd-group xml:lang="pt" kwd-group-type="author-generated"><kwd>sujeitas e sujeitos periféricos</kwd><kwd>racionais MC’s</kwd><kwd>consciência periférica</kwd><kwd>epistemologia periférica</kwd></kwd-group><kwd-group xml:lang="en" kwd-group-type="author-generated"><kwd>periphery</kwd><kwd>peripheral subjects</kwd><kwd>Racionais MC’s</kwd><kwd>peripheral consciousness</kwd><kwd>peripheral epistemology</kwd></kwd-group><counts><fig-count count="0"/><table-count count="0"/><equation-count count="0"/><ref-count count="25"/><page-count count="18"/></counts></article-meta></front><back><ref-list><ref id="B1"><element-citation publication-type="journal"><article-title>Em busca do urbano</article-title><source>Novos Estudos Cebrap</source><date><year>2009</year></date><issue>83</issue><person-group person-group-type="author"><name><surname>Arantes